 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 18, 1994, Saturday, Southland Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
