ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: HUNTINGTON BEACH; VINTAGE CARS IN RACE TO BE SHOWN TODAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Fans of vintage cars can get a close look at cars participating in the Great 
American Race during a special display today at Huntington Beach Mall. 
</P>
<P>
 The free event will begin at 10 a.m. with entertainment by the U.S. Navy Band. 
The classic autos will be on display from noon to 3 p.m. 
</P>
