 Libby Jason of Coto de Caza has made a business of setting other peoples' 
tables. She does more than just sprinkle dishes around, though. Starting at $15 
a place setting, Your Home Plate brings ideas, plates, silverware and whatever 
else is needed to set a table for a special dinner. If her customers prefer, 
Jason will use their dishes and arrange them with a fresh eye. 
</P>
<P>
 Her tabletop design service includes helping clients plan a theme and coming 
back to take all the pieces away when the party's over. For information, call 
(714) 589-3258. 
