</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Officials announced this week the appointment of Sandra Christopher as library 
services director. 
</P>
<P>
 Christopher, 52, has been assistant library director for the past 11 years. A 
former branch services coordinator and librarian in Burbank, Christopher will 
earn 10% more than she did as assistant director. Her salary will be $71,000 in 
her first year. 
</P>
<P>
