<HEADLINE>
<P>
A NEW APPRECIATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 How wonderful that Knott's Berry Farm's new attraction, Mystery Lodge, is a 
life-affirming blend of old mythology and new technology rather than just 
another cartoon-oriented thrill ride ("Reflection: Lodge's Most Special 
Effect," May 31). 
</P>
<P>
 And isn't it ironic that after so many years of purposely destroying the 
American Indian cultures in the arrogant, ethnocentric belief that we are 
civilizing them, we now turn back to the myth and culture of the Native 
Americans to find a positive lesson of life and family and hope? 
</P>
<P>
 GREGG MILLETT 
</P>
<P>
 Westminster 
</P>
</TEXT>
