<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOGEN NAMED COACH AT CAMARILLO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Liz Hogen was named the girls' soccer coach at Camarillo High, replacing 
Pascual Campos. 
</P>
<P>
 Hogen, 23, who played soccer at Camarillo five years ago, is a former junior 
varsity coach. 
</P>
</TEXT>
