<P>
 Still at KCRW -- Chris Douridas, host of "Morning Becomes Eclectic" on KCRW-FM 
(89.9), has talked with officials at KLIT-FM (101.9) about joining the station 
under a new format but has not formally agreed to do so, as The Times reported 
Thursday. He continues at KCRW. 
